{"tid":2195423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"社區檢測中心已使用醫療廢物散落東廊","createTime":"2020-09-09T07:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T08:03:21.000Z","uid":303304,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e29880a6e9abfae9511bb1d9567fcedf09952181","tid":2195423,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情仍然持續，早前衞生防護中心指社區檢測中心內的廢物與一般家居廢物無異，並不屬於醫療廢物，然而未能釋除市民疑慮。至昨午，有市民發現東區走廊近香港海防博物館有大量已使用的保護衣、保護帽及保護面罩，懷疑垃圾車從檢測站收取垃圾後，該批醫療廢物未有妥善包好，跌在路邊，散落一地，形容情況非常誇張，恐會將病毒散播出社區。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNrT9AX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNrT9AX.png&h=3dcff208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200909/YPOF57X6FZFX5JEHPULFHWAUZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200909%2FYPOF57X6FZFX5JEHPULFHWAUZ4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=034583e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200909%2FYPOF57X6FZFX5JEHPULFHWAUZ4%2F&h=34f77129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200909/YPOF57X6FZFX5JEHPULFHWAUZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"53a34692b0bf06d4114c509b743265fc99375fb0","tid":2195423,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"讀者Kenneth昨午5時揸車沿東區走廊往柴灣方向行駛，駛至香港海防博物館對開馬路時，見到多件保護衣、面罩、口罩及黑色垃圾袋散落一地，之後亦相繼在柴灣IVE、張振興伉儷書院、柴灣公園對開路邊發現保護衣及保護帽，大約兩小時後，他再經過上址時仍見到該批保護衣物在路邊，「今朝經過嗰陣都唔見有，直到去到下晝5點幾行過就見到一大堆保護衣喺路邊，周地都係，見到真係好驚」"},{"pid":"0236d57e19e6d6af9cf9e19d3aed7454ee9c6781","tid":2195423,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"要睇全文請自己訂閣蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fc0c38e8f9dd8ce435792f587ae7202d1505bb","tid":2195423,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse